v 3
d cortable: Custom correlation table exported to RTF (Word)
d
d Computes pairwise correlations and exports a lower-triangle
d correlation table to a Word-compatible RTF file. Significant
d coefficients are bolded at a user-specified threshold.
d Variables are numbered with a legend below the table.
d
d Author: Custom package
d Distribution-Date: 2026
f cortable.ado
